      • testFilled

        @Test
public void testFilled()
        Test a filled grid is already solved. Like all the tests here, it checks three things: - the return value of solve() - that the grid is full of digits - and that it is a valid grid.

      • testBacktrackThrough9

        @Test
public void testBacktrackThrough9()
        Test an arbitrary example which has to backtrack into a solve which successfully placed a nine. Putting the digit clearing in the wrong place can cause such 9s to not be removed on backtracking.
